 Dear Naukri Mili Job Placement India,


 Digital transformation and the growing influence of analytics have disrupted conventional HR practices, demanding a shift in leadership mindset and capability. To thrive in this environment, high-potential HR professionals and aspiring CHROs must position themselves as strategic business partners—leading organisational resilience, growth, and transformation from the forefront.
 
  STARTS ON 
 September 30, 2025
 DURATION 
 8 Months 
 Live Online & Campus Immersion 

 PROGRAMME FEE 
 INR 4,00,000 + GST 

https://click.info.emeritus.org/?qs=5ecc685e20cf27723182e3d14c3953001c0ad94e2ee55df73047e3e5e2fa98cb6f762f638b8c79c9edff25db95cde9115c2f89624e2bb224fb6ff971d6ea7ded 
LEARN MORE 


 In this context, the Senior Executive Development Programme in Building Future CHROs by XLRI VIL, now in its fifth cohort, offers an opportunity to navigate this transition effectively. This 8-month programme, delivered through live online sessions, is designed to help you master the dynamics of strategic HR. This coveted programme equips HR leaders with best practices, strategic insights, and leadership skills tailored to India’s evolving HR landscape—empowering them to drive impact, influence business decisions, and lead with confidence.
 

