 Learn from renowned XLRI faculty known for enabling leadership transformation
 

Engage in 100+ hours of live online learning with XLRI faculty and industry experts

Be part of a legacy-defining B-school renowned for HR leadership and excellence

High-impact curriculum on HRM strategies, financial acumen and more

Network and experience in-person learning during the 7-day campus immersion at XLRI

